<div style="padding-top:80px;">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-5" style="background:var(--gradient-hero);">
    <div class="container py-4 text-center text-white" data-aos="fade-up">
      <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-3">Help <span class="gradient-text-gold">Center</span></h1>
      <p class="lead mb-0" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;">Find quick answers to the most common questions about Trusted Escort India.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row g-5 justify-content-center">
        <!-- Sidebar categories -->
        <div class="col-lg-3" data-aos="fade-right">
          <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm p-3" style="border-radius:var(--radius);position:sticky;top:90px;">
            <h6 class="fw-bold px-2 mb-3">Categories</h6>
            <a href="#browsing" class="d-block px-2 py-2 text-decoration-none text-muted rounded mb-1" style="font-size:.92rem;" onmouseover="this.style.background='#f8f0f2'" onmouseout="this.style.background=''"><i class="bi bi-search me-2 text-primary"></i>Browsing Listings</a>
            <a href="#posting" class="d-block px-2 py-2 text-decoration-none text-muted rounded mb-1" style="font-size:.92rem;" onmouseover="this.style.background='#f8f0f2'" onmouseout="this.style.background=''"><i class="bi bi-plus-circle me-2 text-primary"></i>Posting an Ad</a>
            <a href="#account" class="d-block px-2 py-2 text-decoration-none text-muted rounded mb-1" style="font-size:.92rem;" onmouseover="this.style.background='#f8f0f2'" onmouseout="this.style.background=''"><i class="bi bi-person me-2 text-primary"></i>My Account</a>
            <a href="#safety" class="d-block px-2 py-2 text-decoration-none text-muted rounded mb-1" style="font-size:.92rem;" onmouseover="this.style.background='#f8f0f2'" onmouseout="this.style.background=''"><i class="bi bi-shield-check me-2 text-primary"></i>Safety &amp; Trust</a>
            <a href="#technical" class="d-block px-2 py-2 text-decoration-none text-muted rounded mb-1" style="font-size:.92rem;" onmouseover="this.style.background='#f8f0f2'" onmouseout="this.style.background=''"><i class="bi bi-gear me-2 text-primary"></i>Technical Issues</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Content -->
        <div class="col-lg-8" data-aos="fade-left">

          <!-- Browsing -->
          <div id="browsing" class="mb-5">
            <h4 class="fw-bold mb-4"><i class="bi bi-search me-2 gradient-text"></i>Browsing Listings</h4>
            <div class="accordion" id="accordionBrowse">
              <div class="accordion-item border-0 shadow-sm mb-2" style="border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
                <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#b1">Do I need to register to browse listings?</button></h2>
                <div id="b1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionBrowse"><div class="accordion-body text-muted">No. You can browse all city pages and escort profiles completely free without creating an account. An account is only required if you want to post an advertisement.</div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item border-0 shadow-sm mb-2" style="border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
                <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#b2">How do I search for escorts in my city?</button></h2>
                <div id="b2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionBrowse"><div class="accordion-body text-muted">Go to the homepage and scroll to the city grid. Click your city to see all approved escort service listings in that city. You can also type <strong>/escorts-service/city-name</strong> directly in the address bar — for example <a href="/escorts-service/delhi">/escorts-service/delhi</a>.</div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item border-0 shadow-sm mb-2" style="border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
                <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#b3">Are all profiles verified?</button></h2>
                <div id="b3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionBrowse"><div class="accordion-body text-muted">Every profile is manually reviewed by our admin team before it goes live. However, we verify content quality and compliance — we cannot independently verify every detail an advertiser provides. Always exercise caution and common sense when contacting anyone online.</div></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Posting -->
          <div id="posting" class="mb-5">
            <h4 class="fw-bold mb-4"><i class="bi bi-plus-circle me-2 gradient-text"></i>Posting an Ad</h4>
            <div class="accordion" id="accordionPost">
              <div class="accordion-item border-0 shadow-sm mb-2" style="border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
                <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#p1">How do I post a free ad?</button></h2>
                <div id="p1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionPost"><div class="accordion-body text-muted"><a href="/auth/register">Register a free advertiser account</a>, fill in your profile details, upload a photo, select your city and services, then submit for admin review. Your listing goes live within 24 hours of approval.</div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item border-0 shadow-sm mb-2" style="border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
                <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#p2">How long does approval take?</button></h2>
                <div id="p2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionPost"><div class="accordion-body text-muted">Most ads are reviewed within 24 hours. During peak periods it may take up to 48 hours. You will see the status change to "Approved" or "Rejected" in your dashboard. If rejected, the reason will be shown.</div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item border-0 shadow-sm mb-2" style="border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
                <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#p3">Why was my ad rejected?</button></h2>
                <div id="p3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionPost"><div class="accordion-body text-muted">Common reasons include: unclear or low-quality images, prohibited content, missing service details, or suspicion of fraud. Review our <a href="/terms">Terms &amp; Conditions</a> and resubmit a corrected ad. If you believe your rejection was wrong, contact <a href="mailto:support@trustedescort.in">support@trustedescort.in</a>.</div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item border-0 shadow-sm mb-2" style="border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
                <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#p4">What image formats are accepted?</button></h2>
                <div id="p4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionPost"><div class="accordion-body text-muted">We accept JPG, PNG, WEBP and HEIC images. Maximum file size is 5 MB. Images are automatically resized. Use a clear, recent, well-lit portrait for best results.</div></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Account -->
          <div id="account" class="mb-5">
            <h4 class="fw-bold mb-4"><i class="bi bi-person me-2 gradient-text"></i>My Account</h4>
            <div class="accordion" id="accordionAcc">
              <div class="accordion-item border-0 shadow-sm mb-2" style="border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
                <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#a1">I forgot my password. How do I reset it?</button></h2>
                <div id="a1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionAcc"><div class="accordion-body text-muted">Currently, password reset is handled by contacting our support team at <a href="mailto:support@trustedescort.in">support@trustedescort.in</a> with your registered email address. We will reset it manually and send you a temporary password.</div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item border-0 shadow-sm mb-2" style="border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
                <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#a2">How do I delete my account?</button></h2>
                <div id="a2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionAcc"><div class="accordion-body text-muted">Email <a href="mailto:support@trustedescort.in">support@trustedescort.in</a> with your registered email address and the subject "Account Deletion Request". We will delete your account and all associated data within 30 days.</div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item border-0 shadow-sm mb-2" style="border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
                <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#a3">Can I have multiple accounts?</button></h2>
                <div id="a3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionAcc"><div class="accordion-body text-muted">No. Each person or business is permitted one advertiser account. Multiple accounts may result in all accounts being permanently suspended.</div></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Safety -->
          <div id="safety" class="mb-5">
            <h4 class="fw-bold mb-4"><i class="bi bi-shield-check me-2 gradient-text"></i>Safety &amp; Trust</h4>
            <div class="accordion" id="accordionSafe">
              <div class="accordion-item border-0 shadow-sm mb-2" style="border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
                <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#s1">How do I report a suspicious listing?</button></h2>
                <div id="s1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionSafe"><div class="accordion-body text-muted">Email <a href="mailto:abuse@trustedescort.in">abuse@trustedescort.in</a> with the link to the listing and details of your concern. We respond to all abuse reports within 24 hours. Trafficking or minor-related concerns are treated as emergencies (2-hour response).</div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item border-0 shadow-sm mb-2" style="border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
                <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#s2">What if I think someone is being trafficked?</button></h2>
                <div id="s2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionSafe"><div class="accordion-body text-muted">Call <strong>1098 (Childline India)</strong> or <strong>112 (Police)</strong> immediately for emergencies. You can also email <a href="mailto:abuse@trustedescort.in">abuse@trustedescort.in</a> — we cooperate fully with law enforcement and have a zero-tolerance policy on trafficking.</div></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Technical -->
          <div id="technical" class="mb-5">
            <h4 class="fw-bold mb-4"><i class="bi bi-gear me-2 gradient-text"></i>Technical Issues</h4>
            <div class="accordion" id="accordionTech">
              <div class="accordion-item border-0 shadow-sm mb-2" style="border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
                <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#t1">My image won't upload. What should I do?</button></h2>
                <div id="t1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionTech"><div class="accordion-body text-muted">Make sure your image is JPG, PNG, WEBP or HEIC and under 5 MB. Try converting HEIC to JPG first. If the problem persists, try a different browser or device and contact <a href="mailto:support@trustedescort.in">support@trustedescort.in</a>.</div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item border-0 shadow-sm mb-2" style="border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
                <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-semibold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#t2">The site isn't loading properly. Help?</button></h2>
                <div id="t2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionTech"><div class="accordion-body text-muted">Try clearing your browser cache and cookies. Make sure your browser is up to date. If the site is down entirely, check again in a few minutes. Persistent issues? Email <a href="mailto:support@trustedescort.in">support@trustedescort.in</a>.</div></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Still need help -->
          <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center" style="border-radius:var(--radius);background:var(--bg-light);">
            <h6 class="fw-bold mb-2">Still need help?</h6>
            <p class="text-muted small mb-3">Our support team typically responds within 24 hours on weekdays.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill px-4">Contact Support</a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
